### [Micah Chapter 6](../../../bib/kjv/mic006.htm#001.md)

[Micah](../../../bib/kjv/mic001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">mic 6:0</span></span>

Overview

[Mic 6:1](../../../bib/kjv/mic006.htm#001.md), God's controversy for
ingratitude; [Mic 6:6](../../../bib/kjv/mic006.htm#006.md), for ignorance,
[Mic 6:10](../../../bib/kjv/mic006.htm#010.md). for injustice; [Mic
6:16](../../../bib/kjv/mic006.htm#016.md), and for idolatry.

